        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Even so, Education Secretary Michael Cardona is calling the deal a win. ‚ÄúI applaud @POTUS for averting a crisis with this deal and for protecting our student debt relief plan in full,‚Äù Cardona ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
